### Health check
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/health


### Get contacts
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/contacts


### Get products
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/products


### Create invoice
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/invoices
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "company_id": 1,
  "customer_id": 1,
  "issue_date": "2026-05-13",
  "due_date": "2026-06-12",
  "currency": "EUR",
  "notes": "First test invoice"
}


### Add line to invoice
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/invoices/1/lines
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product_id": 1,
  "quantity": 2
}


### View invoice
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/invoices/1


### Recalculate invoice
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/invoices/1/recalculate
Content-Type: application/json